g.desc: # Initialize the Store STORE_ID=$(fga store create --name def...
g.text: # Initialize the StoreSTORE_ID=$(fga store create --name default | jq -r '.store.id')# Load the Modelfga model write --store-id=$STORE_ID --file=/tmp/openfga/model.fga# Add Members to Groupsfga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write user:1 member group:1fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write user:2 member group:2fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write user:3 member group:3# Add Group Subgroupsfga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:2 child group:1fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:3 child group:2fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:4 child group:1# Add Group, Group#Member, and Group#Subgroup to Report Relationshipsfga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:1 accessor report:1fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:1#member accessor report:1fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:1#descendant accessor report:1fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:2 accessor report:2fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:2#member accessor report:2fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:2#descendant accessor report:2fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:3 accessor report:3fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:3#member accessor report:3fga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write group:3#descendant accessor report:3# Add User to Report Relationshipfga tuple --store-id $STORE_ID write user:4 accessor report:1# Erase Everythingfga store delete --store-id $STORE_ID
